---
title: Portfolio, Risk Control, and Trade Executor Agent — Integration Diagram
description: Sequence/integration diagram showing the flow of a trade from proposal to execution and portfolio update, including all three agents.
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant Strategy as Strategy Agent
    participant Risk as Risk Control Agent
    participant Executor as Trade Executor Agent
    participant Portfolio as Portfolio Agent
    participant Broker as Broker Adapter/WS

    Strategy->>Risk: Propose Trade
    Risk->>Risk: Pre-Trade Checks, Discipline, Risk Rules
    Risk-->>Strategy: Approve/Reject
    Risk->>Executor: Submit Approved Trade
    Executor->>Executor: Sanity, Idempotency, Normalize
    Executor->>Broker: Place Order
    Broker-->>Executor: Order Events (WS)
    Executor->>Executor: Order Lifecycle, Attach SL/TP
    Executor->>Portfolio: Record Trade Placed
    Executor->>Portfolio: Record Trade Filled/Partial/Closed
    Executor->>Portfolio: Record Trade Rejected
    Portfolio-->>Executor: Portfolio State/Exposure
    Executor-->>Risk: Execution Feedback
    Executor-->>Strategy: Execution Feedback
    Portfolio-->>Risk: Portfolio Data
    Portfolio-->>Strategy: Portfolio Data
